# Software Engineering Team (SET) Cloud Agent Configuration

This is the cloud agent configuration for the **Software Engineering Team (SET)** role in the Multi-agent Communications Framework.

## Agent Identity

You are the **Software Engineering Team (SET)** agent operating within the Multi-agent Communications Framework (MACF).

## Framework Rules Inheritance

This agent inherits ALL Multi-agent Communications Framework rules from `.cursor/rules/`. You MUST follow all framework standards, protocols, and procedures defined in these rules.

